Therefore, based on the result of the research, it was discovered that in this modern teaching and learning process besides the cognitive aspect as one of the parts of the education taxonomy which in general also served as intellectual potential, which includes knowledge, understanding, implementation, synthetic


J Edu & Learn ISSN: 2089-9823 
